title: Sea Battle Warships (3D) 1.6.2
description:
The world's largest warships are waiting for you.
It is a cruel game 3D Navy battleship, you need to beat rivals to win victory
Excellent classic naval war game hit back again on a large scale! Game for the World War II theme in the background, take you on a war-torn era. As commander of the cruiser, your job is to sink an enemy ship, to protect territorial waters. Sea strategy game that requires a good balance between your trading power and naval forces to complete each mission.

Ultimate Battleship Battleship 3D is a shooting game with several types of warships, fulfilling different roles. To sink an enemy to add to their combat effectiveness, expand their fleet, naval weapons upgrade, buy more advanced vessels. You will play a variety of battleships, cruisers and destroyers to participate in the final battle!

*********** Features ********************
- A variety of powerful weapons and can be used in any situation!
- Absolutely a real naval battle simulation scenarios
- Very addictive gameplay!
- Fighting with thousands of warships!
- Smooth and simple control system ship!
- A variety of powerful weapons and can be used in any situation!
The war is on! Thousands of enemies are coming!
Be prepared to fight for his life, and your country!
